query:
INSERT INTO series_references (id, library_id, tmdb_id, title, theme_color, created_at)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    title = EXCLUDED.title,
                    theme_color = EXCLUDED.theme_color,
                    updated_at = NOW()
                RETURNING id
